postIllustrate

public String postIllustrate(String alias,
                             String gitRef,
                             String projectName,
                             String pigScriptName)
                      throws IOException
Run a Pig ILLUSTRATE operation.

Parameters:
alias - Pig alias to illustrate (optional: if not provided, illustrate entire script)
gitRef - version of code (git hash) to use
projectName - Mortar project to use
pigScriptName - Pigscript to use (without path or extension)
Returns:
illustrate_id ID of the illustrate that was requested
Throws:
IOException - if unable to run illustrate on API
